        "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified-1\n\nBuild Failed \n\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/oom-master-commit-lint/6752/ : FAILURE\n\nThe Commit title must follow this pattern \"[WHAT] A title\"\n\nWHAT can be a component name (AAI for example), DOC for documentation, COMMON for common, ...\n\nThe title must start with a capital letter (A in the example) and a space must be set between the end of the topic and the actual title: \"] A title\" ( https://jenkins.onap.org/job/oom-master-commit-lint/6752/ )\n\nLogs: https://logs.onap.org/production/vex-yul-ecomp-jenkins-1/oom-master-commit-lint/6752\n\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/oom-master-verify-helm3.8/935/ : SUCCESS\n\nLogs: https://logs.onap.org/production/vex-yul-ecomp-jenkins-1/oom-master-verify-helm3.8/935\n\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/doc-rules/2543/ : SUCCESS\n\nLogs: https://logs.onap.org/production/vex-yul-ecomp-jenkins-1/doc-rules/2543\n\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/oom-master-checkbashisms-lint/2872/ : SUCCESS\n\nLogs: https://logs.onap.org/production/vex-yul-ecomp-jenkins-1/oom-master-checkbashisms-lint/2872\n\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/oom-master-image-verify/7056/ : SUCCESS\n\nLogs: https://logs.onap.org/production/vex-yul-ecomp-jenkins-1/oom-master-image-verify/7056\n\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/oom-master-pre-commit-lint/2864/ : SUCCESS\n\nLogs: https://logs.onap.org/production/vex-yul-ecomp-jenkins-1/oom-master-pre-commit-lint/2864\n\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/rtdv3-global-verify-master/21907/ : SUCCESS\n\nLogs: https://logs.onap.org/production/vex-yul-ecomp-jenkins-1/rtdv3-global-verify-master/21907",
